item.title: CVE-2018-1386|2024-08-05T03:59:38.598Z -- ibm -- workload%20scheduler
item.description: IBM Tivoli Workload Automation for AIX (IBM Workload Scheduler 8.6, 9.1, 9.2, 9.3, and 9.4) contains directories with improper permissions that could allow a local user to with special access to gain root privileges. IBM X-Force ID: 138208.
